defaultUntil the 
default1970s it was unthinkable that a woman journalist would report on men’s sport. Football is Britain’s national game, 
defaultand, as such
default, is probably a good
default barometer by which to measure the progress of women in sports journalism
default and compare it to media coverage of women’s sports today
default.  
