defaultJacqui Oatley found herself on the news pages when she became the first woman commentator on Match of the Day. Oatley had another claim to fame.  She was a former footballer, forced to retire early through injury, and a massive supporter
default of
default the women’s game while equally an expert on the men’s version.
default 
defaultOver the years she has continued to bang the drum on behalf of women’s football. 
