default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe London 2012 Olympics appears to have been a watershed moment 
defaultfor women’s football 
defaultas far as mainstream
default media is concerned. The Great Britain team was given extensive coverage in print, on radio, on television, on the internet and on social media like Twitter. 
